    ocean_brush: "Ocean brush wash",
    ocean_brush_small_description: "one of the most preferred models in our vast market that we serve because it is very easy to operate and maintain, the running cost is very low and the cost is affordable",
    ocean_brush_large_description: "In our model of ocean car wash machines, there are 2 brushes, 1 vertical and 3 horizontal, and it is one of the most preferred models in our vast market that we serve because it is very easy to operate and to maintain, the operating costs are very low and the costs are affordable. Especially due to its modular structure, our optional accessories can be easily installed according to customer demand.In our machine designed according to the “Swing System”, the pressure of the brush on the surface of the vehicle is controlled, safe and gentle with electronic and electromagnetic safety systems on the side and upper brushes. With the « Soft Start », the soft stopping and starting of the brushed motors is ensured. The speed and load control is secured with the « Inverter System » independent of the movement of the bridge.\n It can wash and dry by applying both shampoo (W-WD models) and polish (WD model) to the vehicles to be washed.\n Our brushed vehicle wash equipment is made from premium brands and all parts eliminate the possible risk of electric shock. \n Ocean X1 model PLC offers different washing programs with its computer control, as well as washing all kinds of vehicles of different sizes (such as passenger car, jeep, van, 50NC van, magirus) perfectly.\n 3 The oceanic brushed X1 brushed car wash is the most preferred model because it is easy to operate and the maintenance and operating costs are very low.\n With its brushed car wash safety features, it perfectly washes all types of vehicles up to 225-250 cm. width and 240-350 cm. height (passenger cars, jeeps, vans, high vans, new type magirus, 50 NC and similar vehicles).\n The oceanic X1 brushed car wash machine is designed according to the « Swing System » (model W 350 trolley Swing system). Safe on the surface of the vehicle with electronic and electromechanical security systems on the side and upper brushes. Smooth, controlled brush printing and “Soft Start” equipment ensure smooth stopping and starting of brush motors. The movement of the bridge is secured by an independent « Inverter System » with speed and load control. Since our OKYANUS X1 model machine has a modular structure like our other models, it is possible to easily mount our optional accessories on the machine without taking up extra space.",
