    Hydro_wash_Brushless_Wash_title: "HydroWash Brushless Wash",
    Hydro_wash_Brushless_Wash_small_description: "HydroWash Brushless Vehicle Wash Machine – is our very special model, it is safe and easy to use model that can only do high pressure washing and profile after drying if desired after chemical application with various programs.",
    Hydro_wash_Brushless_Wash_large_description:"Hydrowash Brushless Car Wash Machine – is our very special yet safe and easy to use model that can only do high pressure washing and profile after drying if desired after chemical application with various programs.\n The HYDROWASH brushless car wash is one of our favorite models because it is easy to use, low maintenance and operating costs and safe for customers who are afraid of brushing. After hot-dip galvanizing and phosphate coating, the rods are coated with electrostatic powder paint and baked. All fasteners used are made of stainless materials. There is a « Number » which indicates the number of vehicles washed in the machines. The automaton is computer controlled and it is possible to make the vehicles perform the desired washing process with different washing programs. The automatic profile provides effective cleaning through the use of a followable pressure wash unit and an emollient and emollient acid based detergent. In machinery, the inverter system provides smooth stopping and starting of the actuator motors. The machine's touchless car wash speed (washing time) can be adjusted by the inverter (speed control system) on the machine's control panel. The same running speed setting applies to the drying system, which is optional equipment. The machine is 380V – 50 Hz.\n\n The entire machine control system receives the command by low voltage (24 V). The electrical and electronic equipment of the machine is Siemens (German) + Tele mechanic (French) or its equivalent brand.\n The HYDROWASH DR 240 brushless car wash washes all vehicles up to 2.40m high and 2.20m wide (Passenger Mount, Van, Jeep, Minibus) with shampoo.\n The HYDROWASH DR 240 touchless car wash can be added with the optional accessories listed below.",
