    tunnel_car_wash_title: "Vehicle wash tunnel",
    tunnel_car_wash_small_description: "Tunnel car washing systems are tunnel car washing systems with conveyors that contain advanced technological developments, have a large volume of washing with shampoo or foam, and different washing equipment can be integrated according to demand",
    tunnel_car_wash_large_description:"Tunnel car washing systems are tunnel car washing systems with conveyors that contain advanced technological developments, have a large volume of washing with shampoo or foam, and different washing equipment can be integrated according to of the request.\n\n PLC On the machine controlled by the computer control system. There are a total of 4 brushes, 1 vertical and 5 horizontal, working with Standart Makine Swing System. The brushes are controlled by a precise electronic printing system which is unaffected by normal voltage changes.\n\n Bodywork elements are hot-dip galvanized, electrostatic powder coated, phosphate coated and corrosion resistant . Brushes, gearboxes, pneumatic and electronic materials are supplied by first-class brands.\nIn our machine, which has a washing capacity of 30-45 pieces per hour, it allows you to do digital tracking with the numberer indicating the number of vehicles washed.\n Optional on the AQUA LINE W model; The length of the body can be increased by adding equipment such as drying, washing of the chassis, etc.\n In the AQUA LINE WD model, 1 set of drying 2×5.5 Hp following the upper profile of the vehicle and 1 set of 2×7.5 Hp fixed side drying are standard.\nThe side Robowash (80 bar pressure prewash robot) is standard in the AQUA LINE WDR model.\n\nThe washing machines of RBH AQUALINE tunnel are a conveyor tunnel system with an intensive washing volume that includes the latest technological developments. Accessories that can apply different washing methods can be added to this system. \n\n AQUA LINE tunnel car wash systems can wash vehicles up to 240 cm high and 210 cm wide by applying shampoo or foam depending on the model.\n AQUA LINE body parts are galvanized against corrosion, phosphate coated then baked by coating with electrostatic powder paint.\nIt has a capacity of 30-45 car washes per hour. The number of vehicles washed is standard. The conveyor group consists of rollers with a corrosion-resistant chain, the speed of which can be changed The drive of the inverter can be controlled by the reducer connected to the motor.\n\nDepending on the addition of optional equipment such as as drying, robowash, washing from the chassis to the W model, the length of the body and the conveyor increases.",
