    Fıratline_Bus_Wash_large_description:"FIRAT LINE bus washing systems are designed for companies with large fleets of vehicles that need to wash many vehicles in a short time. These are fixed installations and the vehicles are washed through them at a constant speed. It can be produced in many different types which vary according to brush groups and wash heights. Horizontal brush, side brush, 45 degree angle top corner brushes, pressure washing belt, emollient belt (dirt softening), chassis washing and drying can be added to these models optional.",
