    Lave_linge_intérieur_de_la_remorque_small_description: "The automatic internal washing system for trailers and containers RBH is produced for the purpose of washing and, if necessary, disinfecting trucks, trailers and the interiors of similar closed vehicles transporting goods and foodstuffs.",
    Lave_linge_intérieur_de_la_remorque_large_description:"The automatic internal washing system for trailers and containers RBH is produced for the purpose of washing and, if necessary, disinfecting trucks, trailers and the interiors of similar closed vehicles transporting goods and foodstuffs. When the robot enters the trailer, it sprays softener detergent to cover the entire interior surface until it reaches the tip, and in turn, it lowers the softened dirt on all surfaces, from surfaces to the floor, with water spray with a pressure of 60 bars. In the dirty water that has landed on the ground, it is thrown from the spray nozzles under the robot by scrubbing it on the back of the trailer with pressurized water. The washing process is carried out fully automatically under the control of an operator and is completed in a short time.",

